DarkMouse::

What ever harmed Quickstrike will come here?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

KitKat::
She turned as Wildfire used the words 'snakebot'.
"Ah HA! So you were playing with my mind you horse's tail!  You 
planted taht idea in my head about Rowdy and used the words snakebot.
I turned back and thought very luodly about the death of the herd of 
horses.  Those were my thoguhts you read. You thought your so clever. 
A wolf is a cunning as any animal out there." She growled.
"DON"T EVER READ MY MIND AGAIN!"

She turned and walked in beast mode over to Quickstrike. "How are you 
feeling there big guy? You doing any better?"
